cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper deals with relatedness and similarity tasks using a knowledge base extracted from Wikipedia. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper deals with semantic similarity and entity relatedness. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper uses DBpedia, an open-source knowledge base extracted from Wikipedia, and discusses creating a Wikipedia article link network. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper analyzes the temporal evolution of the Wikipedia article link network. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with methods for measuring entity relatedness and similarity.
